      <title>受挫的经济学家对美国软着陆和美联储降息抱有希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/chastened-economists-hopeful-for-us-soft-landing-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去几年通胀的过山车之旅让经济学家对自己的预测能力感到自卑，但他们对美国软着陆并最终降低美联储利率抱有希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/chastened-economists-hopeful-for-us-soft-landing-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RMT表示，谈判取得进展后伦敦地铁罢工被取消</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/london-tube-strike-called-off-after-progress-in-talks-rmt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 RMT 工会称，计划于本周在伦敦地铁举行的罢工可能会导致数天的出行混乱，但该罢工已在最后一刻被取消。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/london-tube-strike-called-off-after-progress-in-talks-rmt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:28:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国总理在竞争对手回避的民意调查中延长了她的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/bangladesh-ruling-party-sweeps-elections-boycotted-by-opponents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国总理谢赫·哈西娜（Sheikh Hasina）将保住世界上任职时间最长的女性政府首脑的头衔，此前她的政党在遭到对手和选民抵​​制的选举中横扫了一半以上的议会席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/bangladesh-ruling-party-sweeps-elections-boycotted-by-opponents</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党要求答复，美国国防部长仍在住院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/us-defense-secretary-still-hospitalized-as-gop-demands-answers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周日仍在医院接受治疗，因为他因连续几天未能公开有关选择性医疗手术并发症的情况而面临两党越来越广泛的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/us-defense-secretary-still-hospitalized-as-gop-demands-answers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 16:59:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚总统候选人就国防和外债问题展开争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/indonesian-presidential-contenders-spar-on-defense-foreign-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日晚上，印尼总统竞选者在电视辩论中就外债风险和解决南海争端等问题展开了激烈的辩论，这是二月大选前的第三次辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/indonesian-presidential-contenders-spar-on-defense-foreign-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 16:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在哥伦比亚广播公司民意调查中面临越来越大的边境措施压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/senate-to-present-funding-package-this-week-lawmakers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚广播公司新闻/YouGov 的一项民意调查显示，美国人越来越倾向于采取更严厉的措施来遏制美国与墨西哥边境的移民，尽管人们对边境州将移民北上的做法的看法正在发生转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/senate-to-present-funding-package-this-week-lawmakers-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦为一周地铁罢工造成的旅行混乱做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/london-braces-for-travel-chaos-from-week-of-tube-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于地铁网络罢工导致员工无法上班，伦敦预计将出现一周的交通混乱，预计该市的酒吧和餐馆将损失 5000 万英镑（6400 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/london-braces-for-travel-chaos-from-week-of-tube-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:27:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国宇航局与阿联酋合作建造绕月空间站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/nasa-uae-partner-on-space-station-that-will-orbit-the-moon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国宇航局正在与阿拉伯联合酋长国合作支持一项月球项目，旨在建造第一个绕月球运行的空间站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/nasa-uae-partner-on-space-station-that-will-orbit-the-moon</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列表示已结束加沙北部的主要战斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-07/israel-signals-it-has-wrapped-up-major-combat-in-northern-gaza-as-the-war-enters-its-fourth-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶路撒冷（美联社）——以色列军方表示，它已经结束了加沙北部的主要战斗，并表示已经完成拆除哈马斯在那里的军事基础设施，周日针对该激进组织的战争进入了第四个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-07/israel-signals-it-has-wrapped-up-major-combat-in-northern-gaza-as-the-war-enters-its-fourth-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 08:32:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国核心通胀放缓增强了美联储的乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/world-economy-latest-easing-us-core-inflation-seen-reinforcing-fed-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2023 年接近尾声，美国潜在的价格压力可能会继续消退，这支撑了美联储对通胀路径的乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/world-economy-latest-easing-us-core-inflation-seen-reinforcing-fed-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
